Sheet 1 → ticket

Columns:

cms_id | created_at | closed_at


Sheet 2 → feedbacks
🔹 Formula 1 (Get created_at)
=VLOOKUP(A2, ticket!A:C, 2, FALSE)

🔹 Formula 2 (Same Day)
=IF(INT(B2)=INT(C2),"Yes","No")

🔹 Formula 3 (Same Hour)
=IF(HOUR(B2)=HOUR(C2),"Yes","No")


🔹 Count
=COUNTIF(D:D,"Yes")


